    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six mated to a 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-focused example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced VANOS system, ensuring the variable valve timing remains precise. The suspension geometry is tight, featuring upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers for enhanced lateral stability. Power is delivered via a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip through the apex. The exterior retains its original Titan Silver paint with minor patina, while the interior remains a functional, driver-centric cockpit. A mechanically robust specimen ready for the backroads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
