    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97 Check out this awesome ride that's looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape, ready to hit the road for many more adventures. It drives smoothly, looks great, and has been well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to go, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great owner!",
