    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS stepless variable valve timing to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the M-specific aluminum subframes and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) which provides precise compression and rebound management. This example is in solid driver condition; while it shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been proactively addressed, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity of the drivetrain remains uncompromised for the next owner.",
